{"tid":918105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：領土摩擦不宜上綱上線　不能有每次都有必贏的期待","createTime":"2018-11-27T02:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T17:46:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"94089a313758faae877a80608e093e167faef79c","tid":918105,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"以「直言」見稱的官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進發表評論文章，談論中國的「核心利益」。<br />\n<br />\n當中提到，領土是中國的核心利益之一，但領土的細節性摩擦總是有可能出現，不宜將它們過度上綱上線；又說中國在處理對外摩擦時，有時會「被動些」，「國人大概不能有我們每一次都必須贏的期待。」<br />\n<br />\n文章以〈甚麼是中國第一大核心利益？〉為題，稱中國的第一大核心利益，應是中國實現進一步的經濟社會發展，保持全局性的政治穩定，進而完成中國的現代化。所有其他的利益都應該排在這個第一大核心利益之後。不過到了輿論場上，這一最大的核心利益經常被擠到後面，其他利益被排到了更前面，當中最常見的是領土問題。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，領土也是中國的核心利益，但其高度敏感，具有強烈的「零和性質」，各國、各方的「最大公約數」是共同遵守維持現狀原則。中國大的領土安全是有保障的，麻煩在於存在一些邊界糾紛。當無法通過談判解決問題時，最好的做法就是管控分歧。由於中國有「強大的力量」，對管控邊界摩擦有較強的主動性，領土問題總的來說處於中國掌控中，這方面並不存在大的危機，也沒有走到發展利益前面去的真實急迫性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/263555/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%E7%B8%BD%E7%B7%A8%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2-%E9%A0%98%E5%9C%9F%E6%91%A9%E6%93%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B1%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E9%83%BD%E5%BF%85%E8%B4%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25BB%25B3%2F263555%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2-%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%2591%25A9%25E6%2593%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%259C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B6%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25B4%258F%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25BE%2585&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=58a209ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/263555/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%E7%B8%BD%E7%B7%A8%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2-%E9%A0%98%E5%9C%9F%E6%91%A9%E6%93%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B1%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E9%83%BD%E5%BF%85%E8%B4%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85</a>"},{"pid":"907c86d262bb6af2f401c18fa7a7f241239f9504","tid":918105,"uid":916,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一點也不能少</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f030429685e2b2ea4a44ce15f8f4c74b32b178f","tid":918105,"uid":53687,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"俄鬼子欺人太甚，諗一次，中國海參威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da26e1060940e90c969ce7893e79bb74f584b64","tid":918105,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"一點也不能少呢？的士佬果啲出黎回應下呢篇野啦"},{"pid":"1fc1eb472b00f6d3b515537d9b094f86933318ca","tid":918105,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"胡生呢排咁理性既"},{"pid":"8cf9718f11b0e32c0e69bcecb8b96d8dfa0558e9","tid":918105,"uid":59312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"不能每次都贏<br />\n但最後都係贏家"},{"pid":"d0c2d58028b690cf374b9ef9127adf78998285e0","tid":918105,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"咁講法前排金馬獎D偽人點算好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2af3b3b78820ff45779f8796cc03209464e8b61","tid":918105,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8cf9718f11b0e32c0e69bcecb8b96d8dfa0558e9","tid":918105,"uid":59312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"不能每次都贏<br />\n但最後都係贏家"},"citedB